::Decadel::

	Decadel couldn't leave DarkMouse like that, so he decided to go tell the
great leader, Blackarachnia.

	"Oh, honorable one, the bot named DarkMouse is injured badly, and looks
like she needs some help," He said, hoping that Blackarachnia could do
something for the poor bot.
